HEADWORD: Tear-thumb
<hw>Tear"-thumb`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name given to several species of plants of the genus Polygonum,
having angular stems beset with minute reflexed prickles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Teary</ent>⟦br⟧
